{"tid":2116351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：或接收病人銀紙文件染疫","createTime":"2020-07-20T06:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T06:44:04.000Z","uid":353442,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"233d07a1dc04083bd7a23cd31c49073cf4cff68b","tid":2116351,"uid":353442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"其實銀紙真係好污穢, 找錢番尼又唔可以唔袋, 用電子支付至少減咗層接觸先啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇特意提到有一個可能性值得考慮，指3名職員主要負責收銀以及接收眼科病人文件，即使病人和職員之間有玻璃阻隔，但仍會接觸病人的金錢和文件，而他們每日所面對的眼科病人人數至少有200人。袁國勇認為，如果有一名病人帶有病毒，而職員接觸這名眼科病人的金錢或文件後，不注意衛生觸摸眼睛或未洗手進食，便有機會透過非直接接觸感染病毒。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇亦就「金錢染疫」的可能性闡述更多。他指，與其他地區相比，香港在電子支付方面比較落後，過往他擔任其他公職時，已經提出街市和的士不應使用現金交易，但他明白遠水不能救近火，強調目前市民最重要的是應該注意衛生，不要前往餐廳堂食，「一除低口罩就最危險」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200718/HS4EN67ZVZCJ6BSML275GIRMFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200718%2FHS4EN67ZVZCJ6BSML275GIRMFQ%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=3eadd310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200718%2FHS4EN67ZVZCJ6BSML275GIRMFQ%2F&h=690b4ae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200718/HS4EN67ZVZCJ6BSML275GIRMFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"b2115a3c407206966225077230dfcd786d1fde69","tid":2116351,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"全境封鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2e0cedd30954e419a982211462093dddea5a6c","tid":2116351,"uid":342200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"返工都唔驚，驚銀紙文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"bd83a9f8127945772516daac820420f2ce3e9278","tid":2116351,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"我願意接收所有 有武肺嘅銀紙"},{"pid":"be0b487f33f80f72d5